<item>
            <title>[THRIFT-4464] Potentially server-crashing typo in Python TNonblockingServer</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-4464</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The line&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/thrift/blob/bfba370bf163425823ce7b660f9d123f5fc67c79/lib/py/src/server/TNonblockingServer.py#L177&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/thrift/blob/bfba370bf163425823ce7b660f9d123f5fc67c79/lib/py/src/server/TNonblockingServer.py#L177&lt;/a&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
self._wbuf = self.message[sent:]
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But self.message is never assigned. Maybe should be&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
self._wbuf&#160;=&#160;self._wbuf[sent:]&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;n/a&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
